  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Twin Rooms</strong> sleep up to three people, with twin beds and an extra single bed. </p>
<p><strong>Family Loft Rooms</strong> sleep two to four people. There are twin beds in the main area, and upstairs is a cosy sleeping loft with low ceilings and a further two two single beds.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Located in the main hotel building</li>
<li>Private sauna in every room</li>
<li>Shower</li>
<li>WC</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Tea &amp; coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Mini fridge </li>
<li>TV </li>
<li>Cots (available on request, in advance)</li>
